itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest former Navy SEAL Rob O'Neill as they discuss his effort of helping in transitioning Veterans into life after the military through his Special Operators Transition Foundation, the pride his Dad felt when he found out Rob killed Osama Bin Laden, how Rob thinks this year's election will shake out, his friendship with Kid Rock, and his dream foursome in golf.
